{"tid":2078448,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[年度最佳父親] 印尼男託父照顧愛寵 誰知愛理不理仲炸咗嚟食 [有圖]","createTime":"2020-06-25T05:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T05:05:01.000Z","uid":173200,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd2c983395cb953375b42b17e52ce088d158d709","tid":2078448,"uid":173200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T05:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200619_pl_pet3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200619_pl_pet3.jpg&h=b8ea26d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n印尼一名男子四年前買了一條龍吐珠（亞洲龍魚）當作寵物飼養，後來因為體型太大便送回鄉下託父照顧，沒想到近日卻收到家人消息，珍愛的寵物竟然被其拿去落油鍋炸掉，慘成桌上菜餚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200619_pl_pet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200619_pl_pet.jpg&h=1e213995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據報導，在勿加泗市工作的男子Bayu，4年前在雅加達東部的幹東墟市場以80萬印尼盾（約440港元）買下一條龍吐珠做寵物，然而近日卻崩潰發現，心愛的寵物竟然被父親吃下肚，「我的龍吐珠被父親炸了，牠在芝卡朗市陪伴了我兩年，後來把牠送回老家，父親竟然因為懶得照顧就把魚炸了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200619_pl_pet1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200619_pl_pet1.jpg&h=facf21a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBayu表示，當初因為城市空間太小，才會把愛魚送回鄉下屋企照顧，之前在照片中看到牠恢復健康的模樣還覺得十分欣慰，但時間久了後父親卻越發疏於照顧，開始不餵牠常吃的蜈蚣或蟋蟀，而是改餵簷蛇，現在還把牠給炸了！Bayu心疼表示，「他買的時候是80萬印尼盾，現在一條龍吐珠都已經漲到200萬印尼盾了（約1,100港元）。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-proc.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2020/06/20200619_pl_pet2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-proc.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2020%2F06%2F20200619_pl_pet2.jpg&h=7440264b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n他雖然傷心，但慶幸其他家人沒有跟著一起吃，「我已經放下這件事了，不然一想到父親吃魚的樣子就會覺得很噁心。」據了解，龍吐珠因其金黃色的外型，常被認為能帶來財富與好運而成為高級觀賞魚；牠是一種保留許多硬骨魚類原始特徵的物種，所以也具有古生物研究價值。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6641706-%e5%8d%b0%e5%b0%bc%e7%94%b7%e8%a8%97%e7%88%b6%e7%85%a7%e9%a1%a7%e6%84%9b%e5%af%b5-%e8%aa%b0%e7%9f%a5%e6%84%9b%e7%90%86%e4%b8%8d%e7%90%86%e4%bb%b2%e7%82%b8%e5%92%97%e5%9a%9f%e9%a3%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F6641706-%25e5%258d%25b0%25e5%25b0%25bc%25e7%2594%25b7%25e8%25a8%2597%25e7%2588%25b6%25e7%2585%25a7%25e9%25a1%25a7%25e6%2584%259b%25e5%25af%25b5-%25e8%25aa%25b0%25e7%259f%25a5%25e6%2584%259b%25e7%2590%2586%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%2590%2586%25e4%25bb%25b2%25e7%2582%25b8%25e5%2592%2597%25e5%259a%259f%25e9%25a3%259f&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfVA4V8ywhhxRXFDRWvztIyc%3D&h=ed6a2c5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/6641706-%e5%8d%b0%e5%b0%bc%e7%94%b7%e8%a8%97%e7%88%b6%e7%85%a7%e9%a1%a7%e6%84%9b%e5%af%b5-%e8%aa%b0%e7%9f%a5%e6%84%9b%e7%90%86%e4%b8%8d%e7%90%86%e4%bb%b2%e7%82%b8%e5%92%97%e5%9a%9f%e9%a3%9f</a>"}]}